sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler as /loop (Host Daemon)
    participant LoopAgent as os-learning-loop
    participant Status as context/status.md
    participant Logs as context/memory (L2)
    participant MemMan as os-memory-manager
    participant SkillImprove as os-skill-improvement
    participant LTMem as context/memory.md (L3)

    Note over Scheduler, LTMem: Autonomous Background Heartbeat

    Scheduler->>LoopAgent: Wake up (Every X hours)
    activate LoopAgent
    
    LoopAgent->>Status: Read active tasks & blockers
    Status-->>LoopAgent: Next item in queue
    
    LoopAgent->>Logs: Analyze yesterday's interactions
    LoopAgent->>MemMan: Trigger Memory Maintenance
    
    activate MemMan
    MemMan->>Logs: Parse facts vs ephemera
    MemMan->>LTMem: Conflict Check (Dementia Defense)
    LTMem-->>MemMan: Clear / Conflict
    MemMan->>LTMem: Write New Architectural Rule
    MemMan->>Logs: Archive Log File
    deactivate MemMan

    Note over LoopAgent, SkillImprove: Phase 7 — Skill Improvement Gate
    LoopAgent->>SkillImprove: Any skill routing weakness found?
    activate SkillImprove
    SkillImprove->>SkillImprove: RED scenario → eval gate → REFACTOR
    SkillImprove-->>LoopAgent: KEEP/DISCARD + score delta
    deactivate SkillImprove

    LoopAgent->>Status: Update Timestamp & modify Queue

    deactivate LoopAgent
    Scheduler->>Scheduler: Sleep until next tick
